title: BLACKPINK - 'Kill This Love' Live at Coachella 2019
description:
BLACKPINK performance of 'Kill This Love' from Coachella 2019 featured in the new YouTube Originals documentary, â€œCoachella: 20 Years in the Desertâ€.

Watch on YouTube - http://yt.be/couchella

Premiering only on YouTube April 10, 2020 at 12pm PT
